//i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F23uj2vB.jpg&h=2f20a0b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家快啲嚟上香啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"f67755ceef58bab2cc914361eb0f10bcf081bbef","tid":2045451,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:33:27.000Z","msg":"一係鬼 一係無能廢柴。 兩樣都係拖走。"},{"pid":"0d33452f7628b0ea581d9ac139b78aeec3c30ebf","tid":2045451,"uid":27432,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:37:27.000Z","msg":"台長講得好<br />\ndllm 搞左咁耐就係為呢一刻<br />\n而家先叫有少少成積<br />\n但佢偏偏呢個時刻先出黎講d咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7538e6713663f7c2c269d58db19a6164f94e79","tid":2045451,"uid":15647,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:46:05.000Z","msg":"佢屌尻手足本土勇武係鬼，一早當藍店處理蘋果"},{"pid":"95f847b7696585d5577f0fbcd744ebe9c1a0c9e0","tid":2045451,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60b0490aca0fbef9d387bb4227447ee2a59272f","tid":2045451,"uid":253016,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T00:00:41.000Z","msg":"劉仲敬都講過<br />\n呢堆泛民垃圾同建制垃圾<br />\n基本上就係零作用吸血廢物<br />\n而家係港獨義士眼中佢地就係支那人<br />\n係支那人眼中佢地就係港獨<br />\n掃入垃圾堆係遲早既事"},{"pid":"4381aad06df4f79970514ac1ab3bce58c154999f","tid":2045451,"uid":82655,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T00:07:54.000Z","msg":"日撚日上twitter做任務<br />\n肥佬黎一句收曬我哋皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d75304b067e830b3762525881746f5694d59c3","tid":2045451,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T00:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc22645c5925dd1da3187538cf8af63250483fa7","tid":2045451,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime